data.description: FABULOUS RANCH WELCOMES YOU HOME!  This 3 bedroom, 1 bathroom, 1056 SF Jewel offers loads of updates to make your spring & summer living delightful. A  bright kitchen has generous prep space along with room for gathering around the table.  The cheery living room is equally spacious.  Updates include electrical, furnace, water heater, AC, concrete driveway and patio, bathroom, some windows. Full fenced backyard sports flower beds, room for gardening and play. Plus an 8' x 10'  X-tall shed with loft storage. Break out the grill; get the firepit blazing; surround yourself with family and friends. Come See - you could settle in before summer arrives!  Seller will provide the Certificate of Occupancy at closing plus a 1 yr. APHW home warranty.
